Sableye (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0301: Delcatty
Pokémon
#0303: Mawile →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Sableye (TCG Pocket).

Sableye has been featured on 26 different cards since it debuted in the EX Sandstorm expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Sableye cards are normally Darkness-type or Psychic-type Basic Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Sableye

Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
